rows.label: qst100301_msg0002
rows.name: I'm not okay at all, mo!

rows.label: qst100301_msg0003
rows.name:
Pupun has been doing 40 hours
of flight training to get an
unlimited pilot's license, mo!

rows.label: qst100301_msg0004
rows.name:
Pupun's dream is to pilot my own
ship, travel all over Alst, and
eat all the delicious food...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0006
rows.name:
It's the chorus of the demon of
destruction for my dream, mo...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0007
rows.name:
Even Pupun can't go against the
rumbling tummy demon, mo...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0008
rows.name:
Anything will do, mo... As long
as it's edible, anything...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0501
rows.name:
Thank you, but my tummy
is still not full, mo...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0502
rows.name:
If you don't mind, could
you bring me something
else Pupun could eat, mo?
